      "span_text": "Herd residual variance was weighted by the residual degrees of freedom from model 1 and the average residual variance for all herds from a state was assigned a weight of 20, which is equivalent to the weight assigned to the average regional herdyear variance in heterogeneous variance adjustments for US genetic evaluations  .",
